# Weapons and Combat Tools

Every adventurer needs a reliable way to defend themselves and overcome threats. Your choice of weapon reflects not just practical considerations of damage and range, but your character's fighting style, background, and identity. The greataxe-wielding berserker and the rapier-dancing duelist both work mechanically—they just tell different stories.

Autumn Phoenix RPG organizes weapons into six categories, each offering distinct tactical advantages. All weapons use the same base 2d6 damage system, with variations coming from weapon weight, special properties, and how you wield them.

**Attack Roll:** 2d6 + [Might or Grace] + Combat

